{"tid":1892800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東張西望出陰招搶黃店功勞","createTime":"2020-02-22T18:48:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T16:07:39.000Z","uid":276382,"like":30,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"def889674feae1714907804ab8eaefbbbe68d564","tid":1892800,"uid":276382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T18:48:00.000Z","msg":"今日見到東張西望個廣告<br />\n叫人如果有防疫用品嘅消息<br />\n就打比佢地報料<br />\n目的係想<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">扮抗疫大台</span></span><br />\n黃店就為香港人全世界撲口罩<br />\ncctvb就坐享其成<br />\n報下邊度有口罩就扮有份幫手抗疫<br />\n明明啲報導嚴重失實<br />\n報到日韓好撚大鑊咁<br />\n香港同支那嘅疫情就避而不談<br />\n大家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好</span></span>瘋狂打電話報假料<br />\n熱線係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">60886600</span></span>"},{"pid":"2932ffc5016f5c20d05a638a290e987f82f42e0d","tid":1892800,"uid":343361,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T18:50:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n垃圾台出嘅垃圾節目<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"9bdd67a5e918dd46552adda81a912e4e42ab9393","tid":1892800,"uid":149487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T18:56:45.000Z","msg":"叫楊明個堆奶共明星捐啦<br />\n去撚咗邊呀"},{"pid":"f96313d54a68f6e232b49f2bb76d43c116e2d7cb","tid":1892800,"uid":276382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:11:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ffcd3780195cf2d062ac0261cfaa9244e493fd0d","tid":1892800,"uid":276382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:11:42.000Z","msg":"唔"},{"pid":"bc23184a3c4a512f1ba75e17795783c1e72753cb","tid":1892800,"uid":276382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:11:53.000Z","msg":"到"},{"pid":"d38c0c93772d0071901a428604452e8d5ec32e02","tid":1892800,"uid":276382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:12:07.000Z","msg":"呀"},{"pid":"f393d81dcb00eb0b4c99a06c0c823a70129bb100","t